<p>Paging module. The topmost <code>.paging</code> wrapper is set as an <code>inline-block</code>, so you can center easily by adding <code>text-align: center</code> to the parent container if you want to.</p>

<p>Use <code>.disabled</code> class on <code>.pg-block</code> to disable.</p>

<p>If you want to make a paging module with just the prev/next pager buttons, remove the <code>pg-list</code> inbetween; same thing if you want it vice versa with only the page list.</p>

<br>

